### Implement generateStaticParams for Dynamic Routes in Expo Router

Source: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/router/web/static-rendering.mdx

This TypeScript/React Native snippet demonstrates how to use `generateStaticParams` in an Expo Router dynamic route (`src/app/blog/[id].tsx`) to pre-render pages for known IDs at build-time. The function fetches post data and returns an array of parameters, ensuring static HTML files are generated for each post, which is essential for SEO with dynamic content.

```tsx
import { Text } from 'react-native';
import { useLocalSearchParams } from 'expo-router';

/* @info This method is run in a Node.js environment at build-time. */
export async function generateStaticParams(): Promise<Record<string, string>[]> {
  /* @end */
  const posts = await getPosts();
  // Return an array of params to generate static HTML files for.
  // Each entry in the array will be a new page.
  return posts.map(post => ({ id: post.id }));
}

export default function Page() {
  const { id } = useLocalSearchParams();

  return <Text>Post {id}</Text>;
}
```

### Statically-typed URL Parameters > Rest Parameters with Search Parameters

Source: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/router/reference/url-parameters.mdx

When using rest parameters with search parameters, the rest parameter captures path segments as an array while search parameters continue to be returned as individual string values. This means you can have both dynamic route segments and optional query parameters in the same route, with each being typed and handled appropriately according to their nature.

### Dynamic Route Redirects in Expo Router

Source: https://github.com/expo/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/router/advanced/redirects.mdx

Create redirects for dynamic routes using bracket syntax in source and destination paths. Variable names are matched during redirection; unmatched variables are passed as query parameters.

```json
{
  "plugins": [
    [
      "expo-router",
      {
        "redirects": [
          {
            "source": "/redirect/[slug]",
            "destination": "/target/[slug]"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  ]
}
```

```json
{
  "plugins": [
    [
      "expo-router",
      {
        "redirects": [
          {
            "source": "/redirect/[fruit]/[vegetable]/[meat]",
            "destination": "/target/[vegetable]/[fruit]"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  ]
}
```

